### T4 — GW-04: Curtain wall renderer

  You are implementing GW-04 in a BIM web app (monorepo at /Users/jhoetter/repos/bim-ai).
  Start by pulling main: git checkout main && git pull origin main

  Goal

  When a wall has isCurtainWall: true, render it as a glass curtain wall grid instead
  of a solid box. The existing makeWallMesh must remain unchanged for non-curtain walls.

  Prerequisites (already in main after GW-01 merges)

  isCurtainWall field exists on WallElem (coerced in store.ts).

  Step 1 — add makeCurtainWallMesh helper

  In packages/web/src/Viewport.tsx, add a new function after makeWallMesh:

